properties.name: vehicle.log.access-key-id
properties.description: 日志服务器认证ID

properties.name: vehicle.log.access-key-secret
properties.description: 日志服务器认证密钥

properties.name: vehicle.log.controller-log-enable
properties.description: 是否开启 controller log 日志，默认为 true

properties.name: vehicle.log.custom-mdc-filed-list
properties.description: 自定义 MDC 字段配置，根据自身项目进行日志拆分，显示成单独的字段

properties.name: vehicle.log.datasource-routing-aspect-log-enable
properties.description: 是否开启 datasource routing aspect log 日志，默认为 false

properties.name: vehicle.log.dubbo-consumer-log-enable
properties.description: 是否开启 dubbo consumer log 日志，默认为 true

properties.name: vehicle.log.dubbo-provider-log-enable
properties.description: 是否开启 dubbo provider log 日志，默认为 true

properties.name: vehicle.log.endpoint
properties.description: 日志服务器访问域名

properties.name: vehicle.log.exclude-request-header-keys
properties.description: exclude-request-header-keys 排除header中的元素

properties.name: vehicle.log.exclude-response-header-keys
properties.description: exclude-response-header-keys 排除header中的元素

properties.name: vehicle.log.logger-class-line
properties.description: 日志输出显示行数 默认false，打印行数影响效率

properties.name: vehicle.log.package-prefixes
properties.description: 指定包路径参数 日志输出json格式

properties.name: vehicle.log.profile
properties.description: 当前环境

properties.name: vehicle.log.project
properties.description: 远程日志project

properties.name: vehicle.log.request-attribution-keys
properties.description: requestAttributionKeys，与header相反 默认不输出内容，需要指定要输出的key

properties.name: vehicle.log.request-header-keys
properties.description: requestHeaderKeys 默认输出所有key，指定后只输出指定key

properties.name: vehicle.log.response-header-keys
properties.description: responseHeaderKeys 默认输出所有key，指定后只输出指定key

properties.name: vehicle.log.server-max-length
properties.description: 日志内容最大输出长度

properties.name: vehicle.log.sky-walking-max-length
properties.description: 日志内容最大输出长度

properties.name: vehicle.log.test
properties.description: 测试使用，默认关闭

properties.name: vehicle.log.truncated-enable
properties.description: Log 过长是否按 MaxLength 截取，默认为 true
